      "audioUrl": "audio/bebop_match_start_frank_bebop_convo03_01.mp3",
      "text": "I'm not trying to be rude, but how much of you is\u2026 original you.  Well not original per se but-",
      "duration": 7.082
    },
    {
      "order": 2,
      "character": "Victor",
      "audioFile": "frank_match_start_frank_bebop_convo03_02",
      "audioUrl": "audio/frank_match_start_frank_bebop_convo03_02.mp3",
      "text": "I see where you're going - no, I haven't had to swap out parts yet.  Probobly should.  My left arm keeps popping off, but it doesn't feel right to discard it when I don't even know who they were.",
      "duration": 11.473
    },
    {
      "order": 3,
      "character": "Bebop",
      "audioFile": "bebop_match_start_frank_bebop_convo03_03",
      "audioUrl": "audio/bebop_match_start_frank_bebop_convo03_03.mp3",
      "text": "I hope you find answers.",
      "duration": 1.866
